The paper is about conversational search, which involves information retrieval (IR), natural language processing (NLP), and dialogue systems (DS). Therefore, cs.IR and cs.CL are the most likely categories, as they are directly related to IR and NLP, respectively. cs.AI is also likely, as conversational search involves artificial intelligence techniques. cs.HCI is relevant because the paper discusses user interactions with conversational agents. Finally, cs.LG is a possibility, as the paper mentions using machine learning techniques for the baseline results.
